  "description": "The efferent coding agent on Effect.ts + Bun — bundles the TUI frontend; runs headless too (print/json/rpc). Multi-provider (Anthropic/OpenAI/Gemini), persistent sub-agent context tree, cache-safe context compression, zero-config SQLite history. No React.",
  "license": "MIT",
  "author": "Xand Reed <xandreed@proton.me>",
